    • Method Detail

      • updateEcuExtractByTopLevelComposition

        public void updateEcuExtractByTopLevelComposition(java.lang.String topLevelCompositionRef,
                                                  java.lang.String ecuSwCompositionRef)
        Creates or updates the ECUExtract in the system model based on a top level CompositionType.
        Parameters:
        topLevelCompositionRef - A reference to a top level CompositionType. The ECUExtract is created based on the CompositionType, i.e. all software components which are instantiated below the CompositionType will be part of the ECU extract.
        ecuSwCompositionRef - A reference to an EcuSwComposition. If the reference is not null, the service components which are instantiated within the specified EcuSwComposition will be part of the ECUExtract.
        Since:
        2010.a

      • updateEcuExtractBySystem

        public void updateEcuExtractBySystem(java.lang.String systemRef,
                                     java.lang.String ecuInstanceRef,
                                     java.lang.String ecuSwCompositionRef)
        Creates or updates the ECUExtract in the system model based on a System
        Parameters:
        systemRef - A reference to a System. The ECUExtract is created based on the SwcToEcuMapping contained in the System.
        ecuInstanceRef - A reference to an EcuInstance.
        ecuSwCompositionRef - A reference to an EcuSwComposition. If the reference is not null, the service components which are instantiated within the specified EcuSwComposition will be part of the ECUExtract.
        Since:
        2010.a
